### Cloud Run configuration by scale target

| Target | Memory | CPU | Concurrency | Max instances | Min instances |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Prototype | 512Mi | 1 | 10 | 3 | 0 (scale to zero) |
| Startup | 2Gi | 2 | 80 | 20 | 1 (avoid cold start) |
